*(13)ASSEMBLY DRAWING OPTIONS:
*
*Option  Id  DWG  Description
*------  --  ---  -----------
  '-'     1       Not Used.
  '8'     2       Dimensions on dwgs: 1=in.dec, 2=ft-in-frc, 3=ft.dec, 4=in-frc
  '8'     3       Units on thickness: same as 2.
  '2'     4       Use gage(1), do not use gage(2)
  '2'     5       Dimensioning: (1)=Arrows, (2)=Tick Marks
  '1'     6       Show slot/hole&dim(1),show slots(2&4),no slots(3),Sho&Lbl(5)
  '1'     7       Show section through member:(1)=Yes,(2)=No
  '1'     8  ASM1 EP Drawing :(1)=magnify len & offset holes, (2)=to scale
  '2'     9  ASM1 EP Loc  Dim:(1)=Detail, (2)=Drawing
  '2'    10  ASM1 EP Loc  Dim:(1)=End Of Plate, (2)=center of hole
  '1'    11  ASM1 EP Hole Dim:(1)=Cumm dim,(2)=spacing dim,(3)no dim.[NA]
  '1'    12       Plate Table:(1)=Full ,(2)=No Webs,(3)=None 
  '2'    13       Plate Table Quantity & Weight:By building(1),By Fab Piece(2)
  '3'    14  ASM1 Control OF  Dim: (1)=yes, (2)=none
  '2'    15  ASM1 Control IF  Dim: (1)=yes, (2)=none
  '2'    16  ASM1 Control EP  Dim: (1)=yes, (2)=none
  '2'    17  ASM1 Control Ext Dim: (1)=yes, (2)=none
  '2'    18  ASM1 OF len Dim: (1)=individual, (2)=combined, (3)=None
  '2'    19  ASM1 IF len Dim: (1)=individual, (2)=combined, (3)=None
  '1'    20  ASM2 OF,IF,EP,ST Label:(1)=Mark,(2)=Part,(3)=Plate
  '1'    21  ASM2 Web         Label:(1)=Mark,(2)=Part
  '2'    22  RFA  Hole loc on web meas'd from end    :(1)=fab,(2)web 
  '2'    23  RFA  Hole loc on out flg meas'd from end:(1)=fab,(2)flg
  '2'    24  RFA  piece & hole loc on in flg meas'd from end :(1)=fab,(2)flg
  '2'    25       Material Codes: (1)=Use, (2)=No
  '2'    26       welded clips:(1)=label each clip,(2)=label 1 & call (Typ)
  '2'    27  ASM2 Dim to flg brc clips:(1)=none,(2)=top of flg to flg br hole
  '1'    28  ASM2 Web Clip (1)=Rect, (2)=Sloped Top,(3)=T type
  '2'    29  ASM2 Const dep col w/ V splice, dim flg + spl pl:(1)=N,(2)=Y [NA]
  '2'    30  ASM2 Label plate insert points: (1)=Yes, (2)=No [for automatic fab]
  '2'    31  ASM3 Draw end slopes (1)=yes, (2)=no,  (3)=end slope with degrees
  '3'    32  ASM3 EP Weld Options (1)=On Drawing, (2)=None
  '3'    33  ASM3 Web-Flange Weld (1)=On Drawing, (2)=None
  '3'    34  ASM3 Web Butt Welds  (1)=On Drawing, (2)=None
  '3'    35  ASM3 Flg Butt Welds  (1)=On Drawing, (2)=None
  '2'    36  ASM3 Place letter for weld note on drawing: (1)=Yes,  (2)=No
  '1'    37       OF flange hole dim: (1)=from end of flg, (2) dim across bend
  '1'    38       IF flange hole dim: (1)=from end of flg, (2) dim across bend
  '2'    39  RFA  Loc of welded plate on web meas'd from end    :(1)=fab,(2)web 
  '2'    40  RFA  Loc of welded plate on out flg meas'd from end:(1)=fab,(2)flg
  '1'    41       Combine flange lengths at depth change: (1)=No, (2)=Yes
  '1'    42  ASM3 Show dimensions for stiffener at col-raf splice:1=yes,2=no
  '1'    43       Member table to be "Thick x wid"(1), "Wid x Thick" (2).
  '2'    44       Member table to include horizontal lines? 1=no, 2=yes
  '2'    45 ASM3  Clips called out with "NS/FS" ? 1=no, 2=yes
  '1'    46 ASM3  Location of flush clips measured from plate: hole(1), edge(2).
  '2'    47 ASM4  To add the TAPE or TAIL label for dim along either flange.
  '1'    48 ASM4  Shape of stiffener between bolted end plate and flange: 1=std
  '2'    49 ASM4  '2' use circle to show dimension location for clips.
  '1'    50 ASM4  '2' if a detail of web holes is shown on the ASM dwg.
  '2'    51 ASM3  Qty of extra blank lines to add to the ass'ly dwg member table
  '2'    52 ASM3  '2' to ref the web clips from the center of the web on cross section 
  '1'    53       '2' dimension all web slot offsets 
  '-'    54       '1' show vertical maximum dimensions 
  '-'    55       '2' dim on each end of the mem that are perpendicular to outside flange 
  '-'    56       '2' vertical dimensions on front face of member
  '1'    57       '2' spacing dim for welded clips on top flange 
  '3'    58 ASM5  Option to report Hot Rolled member cut length at Outside Flange
  '-'    59       Open 
  '2'    60       sloped flange clip, label angle by (1)pitch symbol,(2) length across clip
  '-'    61
  '-'    62
  'N'    63